name: NØNOS
description: NØNOS is a next-generation operating system built from scratch in Rust.RAM-resident, cryptographically hardened, with anonymous networking via Anyone SDK. NØNOS represents a fundamental reimagining of operating system design, built from the ground up in Rust with privacy, security, and modularity at its core. Our systematic approach to building the world's first dual-architecture operating system. Each phase represents rigorous engineering with Anyone Protocol integration and zkProof security. NØNOS ($N0NOS) deploys through two strategic phases ensuring transparent distribution and long-term token integrity across Solana and Ethereum networks.
